{"tid":1395643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"艾未未: 中國就像一個過度發育的巨嬰","createTime":"2019-08-01T22:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T23:32:19.000Z","uid":284284,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4d06274486f9f476033541f543ed5289e5d5eadf","tid":1395643,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T22:21:51.000Z","msg":"點解呢個咁正嘅soundbite竟然冇乜人廣傳嘅???<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Ai Weiwei: &quot;China is like an overgrown baby which has not yet been equipped with knowledge or rationality. Its judgement is often incomprehensible.&quot;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以我英文能力嘅理解就係:<br />\n<br />\n艾未未: 中國就像一個過度發育的巨嬰<br />\n雖然體型龐大，但頭腦上並未成長過<br />\n沒有知識，也沒有理性思維<br />\n它的判斷和行為，是正常人角度所不能夠理解的<br />\n<br />\n如果翻譯做香港廣東話就係：<strong>點解你做咗幾廿年人仲係可以咁撚on9嘅 ?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/07/30/interview-i-hongkonger-artist-ai-weiwei-supports-citys-brave-clever-beautiful-protest-movement/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2Finterview-i-hongkonger-artist-ai-weiwei-supports-citys-brave-clever-beautiful-protest-movement%2F&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=986c79e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/07/30/interview-i-hongkonger-artist-ai-weiwei-supports-citys-brave-clever-beautiful-protest-movement/</a>"},{"pid":"6f5068ba70652e4f6116ad56eb92ba81b77b4ecf","tid":1395643,"uid":174507,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T22:25:04.000Z","msg":"智障巨嬰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb3aacaaa9578a1ccbf855d4deda5f94e25de38","tid":1395643,"uid":192754,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T22:32:21.000Z","msg":"千與千尋"},{"pid":"c3675996b6fbcb6b6c6ef980864a27cba5f63a34","tid":1395643,"uid":284284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":